_sText:
It took more than 3 years, but here it is: surf_calamity2. It's the sequel to surf_calamity (http://gamebanana.com/css/maps/86340).

Staged skillsurf-map without a jail, obviously designed for surf timers.

Thanks to everyone helping me with this project, I think it turned out well.

I hope you enjoy it!
